Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.91,0:00:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野美星  修学旅行结束回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.14,0:00:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色友人  六花亭的巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶油三明治  当地的kitty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木雕人偶和钥匙圈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道产的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:18.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  我还带来了这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吸吸看…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北海道的香气…闻到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闻不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  回家路上小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.58,0:02:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.94,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就按照预定计画好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过身体没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事哦  那么就11点在站前广场哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么怎么  明天有什么事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不晓得…为什么要问我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是放假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.85,0:02:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是在白天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有点怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  反正是以前就认识的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道小夜学姐也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.36,0:02:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天？  我没有什么计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我倒是觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说下  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说为什么大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  我是为了大八木啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…被江户川同学喊过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先…先说清楚了  我只是碰巧过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是来买书顺便过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  快看  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么来看就是在约会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是约会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得变得好像是了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我也差不多该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都来到这里了  就只有一路跟到底了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打算去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在到了哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部…部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:04:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是是是是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.47,0:05:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也超想跟着他们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说嘘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这样…昨天好好问问他们的计划就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法啊  现在是要跟着这边的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总觉得果然草间老师才是理解她的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…也不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.78,0:05:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去站前取照片的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得奇怪就跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.33,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你们在想什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘  喂  要下车了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这样的组合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.11,0:06:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗  草哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  大概是错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…只是从这边路过而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们再往深处去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.71,0:06:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿高跟鞋走这条路好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还有一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  今年我们也来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  大吃一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我的话就一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全…我完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔…怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测会回家的路上出了交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是现在这个时节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着说今年要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.64,0:07:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果妈妈总是因为太忙来不了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.74,0:07:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像总是自己一个人来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.16,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢  让你们吃惊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是肯定…爸爸会很开心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到小朔和大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星爸爸的手很大  总是开着不知道是真是假的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时也会跟我和美星一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢美星  总是看着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开这个小镇以后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.56,0:08:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为小镇还像原来一样没有变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.34,0:08:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得还会一直保持这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这个小镇里的只有我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的还是会维持原样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定大家都会这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小美星说过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年和小朔一起看流星了  好高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…和大家在一起…我想她真的会很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天已经全黑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  要来我家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.21,0:09:20.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来明天也是晴天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  昨天的模拟考试好难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实话说在校外考试还是头一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是近江同学介绍我去的补习学校的考试
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在近江同学旁边的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是所谓的应试战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看  好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.55,0:10:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天部长从近江同学那里拿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水星凌日的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们也要加油了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…做什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我今天要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔？  江户川同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法  对大家来说那还只是前一天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是想要逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是不知道该如何面对她的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美总是在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我能做的事是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请带回各自班级讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖了这么晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到以前从来没有感觉过的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发愣的灵气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行的手信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是前天给他就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过迟了一晚而已…却感觉已经失去了时机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给男生送书签当手信…不会有什么奇怪的意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么了…当我没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样随着天亮而会变得渐渐难以送出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里读过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点送给他吧  只不过是手信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没有其它意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐  来得刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部的样子好像怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.73,0:12:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天文部  早就很怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学和美星学姐他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然间变得很恩爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  我是蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.38,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  美星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.21,0:12:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着美星学姐的那厌倦的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前都没有出现过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  又变得更难送出了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天之内还送不出去的话  就不送了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.28,0:13:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,委员会的工作吗  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.50,0:13:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰你一下可以吗  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  会长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是眼镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用介意  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到家的话还有后备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.25,0:14:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉成同学和和泉同学都已经回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  就这样回去没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那是校长像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.83,0:14:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样被明野看到的话会不会想歪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.65,0:14:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…和美星同一间小学的话应该是经过住宅区的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前住地方也是那边的住宅区
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和小美…美星同一间公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在啊  伊藤商店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里变成了公寓了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,游乐设备好小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不由得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看不到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.74,0:14:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到了这个小镇后  都没有好好地追寻昔日的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不早点来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么就不待在这个小镇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜坏掉真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个  北海道的手信  兼文化祭的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.15,0:15:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有很多不懂的地方  但不介意的话可以找我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在的脸  我不想看到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.03,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为学生会长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.90,0:15:32.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.26,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Papo君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木同学？  真巧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.60,0:15:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来就我们来送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴塚学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以找你商量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  今天也没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明上次考试的时候大家都集中起来温习
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔在生我气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我隐瞒了他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是传达不了「我很精神  不用担心」了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  叫别人不要担心的时候要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.59,0:16:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少还是有点限制  但好像已经被认可使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好地想  就只有「这次」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.63,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真的要这样做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都已经做好调查了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也都问了其他学校的人  确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是令人费解呢  天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那赶快来准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩…剩下的我自己来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系  我们也想帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真热心呢  明野会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.32,0:17:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直到最近才知道  美星的爸爸的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这么地仰慕他  所以绝不会觉得没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我却什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定做了很多无神经的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小美…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说她很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起看流星雨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上几乎没有看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在电话里说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了这些之后  我所力所能及的就只有这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我们都听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大…大八木同学你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能抑止一定要做些什么的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.03,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干那种事的话也算上我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜学姐  部长？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家  要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  我该怎么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔  我说啊  我…很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸的事也不是不想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来虽然很那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是流星雨的团体观测会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就能够好好地一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试的忘记了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是双子座流星雨的极大日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家都偷偷地做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞒着我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.11,0:20:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我就只能想出这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.66,0:20:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很寂寞  很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是不想遇到坏天气而让你失望而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我也知道这样完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.72,0:20:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  明明是个老女人为什么要这么哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看  可以坐在被炉里吃着蜜柑看星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  大家都为我举办了观测会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着要一起来看星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星  有很多星星在流动着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天美星能和大家一起看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\pos(331,435)}Pollux
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.40,0:21:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21分30秒  北河三方向2等级
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.01,0:21:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:15.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说起来  还真是超现实啊  这个画面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好温暖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小朔  我经常从小朔的嘴边听到爸爸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到现在爸爸就活在小朔的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我不是故意隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  牵起手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.11,0:21:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那里的天空是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好  很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.79,0:22:00.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢  大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱的力量  这是爱的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.14,0:22:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我从刚才就在说  他们两个没有在交往的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.73,0:23:46.65,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪漫追星社
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:49.12,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回  那就像纯白的雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:50.08,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
